    "course_title": "ACTING I: INTRODUCTION TO ACTING",
    "description": "Provides a basic introduction to the craft of acting. Develops disciplines and tools of the actor as they relate to voice, movement, language skills, and engaging communication. Explores how actor training skills can be a benefit in a wide context of professional and personal endeavors.",
